Bandar Raya Plans to Sell Properties for 430 Million Ringgit

-- B y   D i n a k a r   S e t h u r a m a n
-- 
2011-09-19T12:23:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/bandar-raya-plans-to-sell-properties-for-430-million-ringgit.html
Bandar Raya Developments Bhd. (BRD)  has
agreed to sell CapSquare Retail Centre, Permas Jusco Mall,
Bangsar Shopping Centre and Menara BRDB for a combined 430
million ringgit ($138 million) to Ambang Sehati Sdn., subject to
the signing of relevant agreements, it said in a statement to
the Kuala Lumpur Stock Exchange today.  Bandar Raya will distribute part of the proceeds of the
proposed disposal to ordinary sharehoders via a net cash
dividend 80 sen per share, it also said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dinakar Sethuraman in Singapore at 
 dinakar@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sunil Jagtiani at 
 sjagtiani@bloomberg.net  